{"tid":1211442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國對香港發出旅遊警示","createTime":"2019-06-12T15:45:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T15:45:16.000Z","uid":133680,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a800665597afcb6a89c1dc4fa0fbafecbba7bc8a","tid":1211442,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:45:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/420361564693683/posts/2413016642094822/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F420361564693683%2Fposts%2F2413016642094822%2F&d=o1jNmZJj5m3DpFdm5BDgvxZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=4d9547d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/420361564693683/posts/2413016642094822/</a><br />\n【指反逃犯條例示威情況不可預測 英國對香港發旅遊警示】<br />\n<br />\n反對《逃犯條例》示威持續，英國政府今日（6月12日）對香港發出旅遊警示（Foreign travel advice）。<br />\n<br />\n英國政府的網頁提到，於6月9日，有大規模反對《逃犯條例》的示威。到6月12日，大型示威活動集中在立法會大樓和金鐘一帶，導致周邊道路封閉，擾亂公共交通。從下午較後時份，警察和抗議者之間發生了暴力衝突。<br />\n<br />\n聲明指由於情況仍然不可預測，遊客應該避免涉及相關示威。又提到未來幾周可能會有進一步的示威活動，或影響城市大部分區域並影響公共交通，應該保持警惕，並遵循當地政府建議。<br />\n<br />\n全文︰<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/06-12-2019/53587\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F06-12-2019%2F53587&d=o1jNmZJj5m3DpFdm5BDgvxZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=c2a941f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/06-12-2019/53587</a><br />\n<br />\n#旅遊警示 #逃犯條例<br />\n<br />\n請支持PassionPrime：<br />\n<a href=\"http://passiontimes.hk/prime/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpassiontimes.hk%2Fprime%2F&d=o1jNmZJj5m3DpFdm5BDgvxZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=6d5f865e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://passiontimes.hk/prime/</a><br />\n<br />\n請支持熱血時報印刷版︰<br />\n<a href=\"http://passiontimes.hk/4.0/regform.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpassiontimes.hk%2F4.0%2Fregform.php&d=o1jNmZJj5m3DpFdm5BDgvxZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=4f943757\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://passiontim